sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant S as Service Instance
    participant R as Redis
    participant L as Local Cache

    C->>GW: Bearer token request
    GW->>S: Forward request
    S->>L: Check local revoked-jti cache
    alt cache miss
        S->>R: Query revoked:jti
        R-->>S: not revoked
        S->>L: cache(jti=allowed, ttl=20s)
        S-->>GW: allow
    else cache hit revoked
        S-->>GW: deny 401
    end

    Note over R,S: On revoke, convergence depends on cache TTL, pub/sub lag, and retry behavior
